#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/split-gpg-2.rst:119
#: 17fdae3ac0a8471996501d4cf43847fd
msgid "Similar to a smartcard, split-gpg2 only tries to protect the private key. For advanced usages, consider if a specialized RPC service would be better. It could do things like checking what data is singed, detailed logging, exposing the encrypted content only to a VM without network, etc."
msgstr ""

